    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/081477a55bdf6cef7a67c7aa3b704da8.poster.avif?t=1745927075\" width=616 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/081477a55bdf6cef7a67c7aa3b704da8.webm?t=1745927075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/081477a55bdf6cef7a67c7aa3b704da8.mp4?t=1745927075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你就是那家著名武器店的老板！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这里是你的王国！每当顾客需要一位可靠的武器大师时，你就是他们的第一选择。在浏览货架时，他们会在店内的每个角落感受到你的独特风格，这家商店正准备在城市中声名鹊起。来吧，把你的商店打造成梦想中的模样！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/006e97d44f418eccaebd575283e0107c.poster.avif?t=1745927075\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/006e97d44f418eccaebd575283e0107c.webm?t=1745927075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/006e97d44f418eccaebd575283e0107c.mp4?t=1745927075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在大师的手中，武器焕然一新！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一把武器都有它的故事，而继续讲述这个故事就靠你了。仔细检查收到的订单，找出问题，并展现你的技能。清洁、修复、更新机制！一步一步，让这些武器在你的手中重获新生！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/c6e58343a92808c305042a80c616ca86.poster.avif?t=1745927075\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/c6e58343a92808c305042a80c616ca86.webm?t=1745927075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/c6e58343a92808c305042a80c616ca86.mp4?t=1745927075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>焕然一新：清洁且准备就绪！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是旧步枪还是现代手枪，每一把武器都值得第二次机会。先清洁武器，然后熟练修复它们。更换零件并恢复损坏的机制。现在，这把武器又可以大放异彩了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/722de707f4dcf6267a4cb1b4128c7731.poster.avif?t=1745927075\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/722de707f4dcf6267a4cb1b4128c7731.webm?t=1745927075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/722de707f4dcf6267a4cb1b4128c7731.mp4?t=1745927075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>最后一环：射击测试！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一把修复过的武器都值得一次试用。前往靶场，扣动扳机，测试它的清洁度和精准度。这些测试是证明你的专业水平的最佳方式。另外，几个精准的射击也会让你倍感乐趣！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/632c84b93c264c78d259d8b4bf1b0464.poster.avif?t=1745927075\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/632c84b93c264c78d259d8b4bf1b0464.webm?t=1745927075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3195310/extras/632c84b93c264c78d259d8b4bf1b0464.mp4?t=1745927075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
